            </rs>. Aged 11. - <rs id="t18340703-135-punish746" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18340703-135-punish746" type="punishmentCategory" value="transport"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18340703-135-defend840 t18340703-135-punish746"></join>
               Transported for Seven Years
            </rs>.</p>
